01:03:28,169 --> 01:03:31,551
And so that leaves us, in some cases, with more questions.

620
01:03:32,851 --> 01:03:35,753
And I know that, frankly, sometimes with these budget discussions,

621
01:03:36,599 --> 01:03:42,143
I think everyone's a little more comfortable if we either come in and say the sky is falling and everyone has to panic.

622
01:03:42,724 --> 01:03:46,467
