01:04:10,882 --> 01:04:16,184
If our increase is below $3 million, that is going to be a significant, significant challenge.

629
01:04:16,704 --> 01:04:23,986
If our increase is above $6 million, we're going to have to do some additional strategic planning, frankly, to make sure that we're making the most of the investment.

