01:04:24,566 --> 01:04:26,887
Somewhere within that range, in 3.4 to 5.8,

631
01:04:29,229 --> 01:04:40,455
is a number in which we will be able to make good on the investment, maximize those resources to benefit students, and also these sound fiscal stewards.

