01:06:50,014 --> 01:07:09,486
So in the flow chart that we had worked on together, I was under the impression that the process around when the city appropriation, how it goes, what happens if the school committee votes yes, what happens if the school committee votes no, whose decision it is, where it goes, because we don't have any information on that.

660
01:07:09,527 --> 01:07:09,607
And

